♪If the sea didn't wait
for the evening breeze♪

508
00:26:38,370 --> 00:26:41,170
♪And swim with me to you♪

509
00:26:41,220 --> 00:26:44,760
♪I'd become♪

510
00:26:44,910 --> 00:26:47,820
♪A whale
who forever keeps the sea company♪

511
